{With 11 points and a good suit you should make a positive response. So you bid 2\H. Partner then says 4NT. What is your bid? 

The 4NT bid agrees \Hs as trump. You have one Key-Card, the \HK, so you bid 5\C. Partner bids the \H slam.}

